  "content": "<div>\n<div>\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.elpais.com.uy/noticias/premium\">\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"Logo el pais +\" src=\"https://el-pais.brightspotcdn.com/aa/0e/aeb5ec75407e934f037f101d8080/logo-ep-blanco.svg\" />\n</picture>\n</a>\n<p>\nHay que leer\n</p>\n<h2>Crónica sobre el idealismo, el desarraigo y un doloroso retorno al paisito</h2>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><figure>\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"López Belloso.jpg\" srcset=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/0c44531/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1368x941+0+213/resize/1440x990!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2Fe0%2F84%2Feab635eb48eeb27865bc66073048%2Flopez-belloso.jpg 1x, https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/22221ce/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1368x941+0+213/resize/2880x1980!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2Fe0%2F84%2Feab635eb48eeb27865bc66073048%2Flopez-belloso.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/0c44531/2147483647/strip/true/crop/1368x941+0+213/resize/1440x990!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2Fe0%2F84%2Feab635eb48eeb27865bc66073048%2Flopez-belloso.jpg\" />\n</picture>\n<p>\n</p><figcaption>Roberto López Belloso</figcaption><p></p>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p><b>Hijos de África</b>, de Roberto López Belloso<b>,</b> relata en modo crónica la historia de un grupo de militantes de izquierda uruguayos que se fueron a Angola entre 1977 y 1986 para tratar de crear comunidad <i>“con palas y lápices”</i>, en medio de una guerra, con carencias increíbles y mientras el universo socialista se hacía pedazos. Una historia de idealismo, desarraigo y doloroso retorno a Uruguay. <i>(Fin de Siglo)</i></p><div>\n<figure>\n<picture>\n<img alt=\"Hijos de África tapa.jpg\" srcset=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/2f0a78d/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2159x3001+0+0/resize/1036x1440!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F51%2F2f%2Fece441db4d5c98492b2745305e1e%2Fhijos-de-africa-tapa.jpg 1x, https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/e1a1f6b/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2159x3001+0+0/resize/2072x2880!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F51%2F2f%2Fece441db4d5c98492b2745305e1e%2Fhijos-de-africa-tapa.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://imgs.elpais.com.uy/dims4/default/2f0a78d/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2159x3001+0+0/resize/1036x1440!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fel-pais-uruguay-production-web.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com%2Fbrightspot%2F51%2F2f%2Fece441db4d5c98492b2745305e1e%2Fhijos-de-africa-tapa.jpg\" />\n</picture>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p>¿Encontraste un error?</p>\n<p>\nReportar\n</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
